  "title": "CIVIL ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will lead on-site project oversight to ensure successful delivery of instrumentation services, driving timely reporting and quality assurance to meet client and project objectives.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Lead on-site project activities to ensure adherence to project timelines and objectives</li><li>Prepare and deliver comprehensive project progress reports and guide decision-making</li><li>Communicate clear, specific instructions to project teams to align efforts with project goals</li><li>Liaise effectively with clients and participate in on-site meetings to maintain strong relationships</li><li>Manage the Quality Assurance & Quality Control (QA/QC) processes to ensure delivery of high-quality products and services</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor Degree in Civil Engineering or equivalent</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Demonstrate independence, self-motivation, and responsibility in managing project tasks and team coordination</li><li>Exhibit a positive and professional working attitude to foster a productive work environment</li></ul>",
